{"page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Pegasystems Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Business Process and Customer Relationship Management\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Pegasystems will work alongside partners and customers to improve their efficiency and service to meet the opportunities of Digital Government through Business Process and Customer Relationship Management (BPM/CRM) solutions using the Pega Platform. The service comprises capturing requirements, designing and configuring the software solution, system deployment and customer on-boarding.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Model driven integrated architecture provides more efficient and faster change\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Customer Engagement, Work Process Management, and Case Management solutions\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Debt and Collections Management, Error, Fraud, and Compliance Management solutions\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Platform provides for extended wrap and replace of legacy applications\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enables re-use for rapid delivery and adopts open standards\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Case and customer-centric providing single view of the case/customer\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Unified, model driven, architecture and workflows with process automation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Data-driven decision making utilising predictive and reactive analytics\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Omni-channel capabilities to support mobile and social collaboration\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Intuitive user interfaces encompassed within intent-led applications\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Cost reduction through automated processes and improved customer service\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Rapid, user-centric, configuration of solutions\u2019 enabling early benefit delivery\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     The processes and solutions can be refined by customers\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Close collaboration with customer delivers alignment to business need\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Customer experience enriched through optional standardised or specialised processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Exploits existing investments via integration and reuse of systems\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Insight into customer behaviour informing user guidance and decision support\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     High performance scalable cloud solutions with mobile and social integration\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improved collaboration and compliance activities across the organisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Optimised use and consistency through guided processes and procedures\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3600 to \u00a31800 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/585509/5207200012173312-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/585509/5207200012173312-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/585509/5207200012173312-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/585509/5207200012173312-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vi\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 6\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      5207\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      2000\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      1217\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      3312\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       Pegasystems Limited\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-deta