es\n         </li>\n         <li>\n          Pegasystems complies with the U.S.-EU Safe Harbor Framework\n         </li>\n         <li>\n          Pegasystems awarded Top 100 most trusted companies in the US by Forbes in 2014\n         </li>\n        </ul>\n       </span>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <a class=\"return-to-top\" href=\"#content\">\n    Return to top \u2191\n   </a>\n  </div>\n </div>\n</main>\n", "company_name": "Pegasystems Limited", "service_id": "5207200012173312", "service_name": "Business Process and Customer Relationship Management"}